title: Diagonal Line
description: A simple graphic featuring a diagonal line that starts from the bottom left and extends to the top right against a black background.

title: Marine Sea Creature
description: A close-up view of a marine sea creature, resembling a large, tubular structure with a textured surface. The creature has a reddish-brown color with lighter patterns and is partially submerged in a rocky underwater environment.

title: Open Scallop
description: A close-up view of an open scallop shell resting on the ocean floor. The shell has a colorful pattern with reddish and cream hues, and the interior reveals the soft body of the scallop.

title: Snail on Moss

title: Colorful Squid
description: A vibrant and colorful squid swimming underwater, showcasing its unique body structure and tentacles against a deep blue ocean background.

title: Abstract Lines

title: Close-up of a Shellfish
description: A close-up image of a shellfish, showcasing its dark, glossy shell partially opened to reveal the inner part. The shell has a smooth texture with a mix of dark and light colors, and the background is softly blurred.

title: Abstract Line Design
description: A simple abstract design featuring a white line that forms a right angle, set against a black background.
